<item>
            <title>[SPR-1584] PortletBean: init-param binding is not lenient</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-1584</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;PortletBean.init method will fail if any init property is invalid/unknown property for the portlet.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The problem is in PortletBean.init method:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;bw.setPropertyValues(pvs);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;should be changed to &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;bw.setPropertyValues(pvs,true);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This will match HttpServletBean &lt;br/&gt;
